lead_paragraph: The U.S. Tennis Association says that 2011 French Open junior champion Bjorn Fratangelo of Pittsburgh has earned a wild-card entry for the main draw at Roland Garros.

headline.print_headline: Pittsburgh's Fratangelo Earns USTA Wild Card for French Open
